&lt;div id=&quot;persaDesc1&quot; class=&quot;hidden&quot;&gt;A persa is a personal data management system.  Most people will use a persa for accessing databases, scheduling, entertainment, and for communication.  Nearly everyone is issued a persa from an early stage in life and will use it for practically every facet of daily life from thereafter. Persas can undergo expensive modifications and upgrades, should the person choose to do so.&lt;/div&gt;\
