&lt;div id=&quot;alleyDesc1&quot; class=&quot;hidden&quot;&gt;The alleyway is obviously narrow.  It has almost enough space for one lane of traffic. Throughtout both day and night cycles, pedestrians and bystanders are wont to loiter near the various businesses that occupy it. Of these businesses, $name&#39;s pizzeria stands unremarkable with its own small neon sign hanging in the window. The sign simply stated &#39;Pizza&#39;. Despite $name insisting that his business does have a name, there is no evidence to support his argument visible on the storefront.

Across the alley and garnering far more attention from anyone to pass by is the rear entrance of a large club.  Multiple gigantic neon signs stand all over the building, including the three that are present in the alley. One of these neon signs exhibits a woman&#39;s face and claims that &#39;the most beautiful women pass through these doors&#39;. It protrudes out into the alley so far that it nearly touches the window of $name&#39;s second story bedroom and fills the frame of anyone whom looks out of it. 

The asphault is still wet from the rain the night previous.&lt;/div&gt;\

Meaning to lock the door behind him, he steps out with one foot then pivots his body and backs into the alleyway.  As he does so, he is caught offguard as his movement is blocked by a large, squishy yet unyielding object.  The object is a belly and the belly belongs to the body of a man nearly two heads taller than $name.

&quot;Whoa, there now&quot; the man says,\
&lt;&lt;if $ch1_isDressed is &#39;true&#39;&gt;&gt;\
&quot;It&#39;s not like you to be meeting me at the door for your delivery.&quot;

$name flips around and squints his eyes in the harsh artificial sunlight, trying to pin a name and face to the familiar voice.  
&lt;&lt;else&gt;&gt;\
&quot;Why don&#39;t you leave that to the professionals?&quot; 
He eyes $name&#39;s nearly naked body and gestures with his head in the direction of the club across the alley.  
